1
00:00:00,367 --> 00:00:03,885
Chairman Lee Jay Hyun
visited CJ 4DPLEX America,

2
00:00:03,886 --> 00:00:07,559
a pioneer of a new moviegoing culture
in the world's largest film market,

3
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:12,379
to encourage employees
and share the company's vision for global growth.

4
00:00:12,379 --> 00:00:14,972
Building on collaborations
with major theater chains,

5
00:00:14,973 --> 00:00:18,644
CJ 4DPLEX has been expanding infrastructure
in the Americas

6
00:00:18,645 --> 00:00:21,784
while advancing content development
and technological innovation

7
00:00:21,785 --> 00:00:24,024
through partnerships with Hollywood Studios.

8
00:00:24,024 --> 00:00:28,224
During the visit, the Chairman toured AMC's
newly opened SCREENX premium theater

9
00:00:28,225 --> 00:00:32,564
and experienced its immersive viewing environment
and technological capabilities firsthand.

10
00:00:32,565 --> 00:00:35,944
He also met with
renowned Hollywood producer Jerry Bruckheimer,

11
00:00:35,945 --> 00:00:40,816
best known for blockbuster franchises
such as “Top Gun” and “F1: The Movie.”

12
00:00:40,817 --> 00:00:42,137
Through a special screening,

13
00:00:42,138 --> 00:00:44,654
the Chairman experienced
the technology firsthand

14
00:00:44,655 --> 00:00:49,349
and exchanged ideas on strengthening
the competitiveness of 4DX and SCREENX.

15
00:00:49,883 --> 00:00:53,795
In addition, he met with leaders
at CJ 4DPLEX America,

16
00:00:53,796 --> 00:00:57,057
who are driving the company's growth
in the Americas.

17
00:00:57,057 --> 00:01:00,271
With rising demand
for premium formats in the region,

18
00:01:00,272 --> 00:01:03,530
he emphasized the importance
of accelerating theater expansion,

19
00:01:03,530 --> 00:01:07,571
securing differentiated content,
and advancing technological capabilities

20
00:01:07,572 --> 00:01:10,696
to evolve into a world-leading
immersive platform.

21
00:01:11,371 --> 00:01:18,011
I think we are the game changer and leader
of worldwide exhibition business.

22
00:01:18,011 --> 00:01:23,483
So I believe we're totally going to change
the exhibition business.

23
00:01:24,051 --> 00:01:25,630
Leveraging the growing recognition

24
00:01:25,631 --> 00:01:28,253
of its premium-format technologies
in the Americas,

25
00:01:28,254 --> 00:01:32,192
CJ 4DPLEX plans to further accelerate
its global expansion.

